31
00:02:55,665 --> 00:02:56,505
It's not your fault.

32
00:02:56,505 --> 00:02:58,145
Why?

33
00:03:24,386 --> 00:03:26,585
You want to kill me for him?

34
00:03:26,785 --> 00:03:29,026
He was my husband.

35
00:03:36,225 --> 00:03:37,466
I am your brother.

36
00:03:37,466 --> 00:03:39,266
I don't have a brother like you.

37
00:05:39,746 --> 00:05:40,705
Why didn't you dodge?

38
00:05:42,346 --> 00:05:44,105
You think you're the lord of Dahuang,

39
00:05:45,145 --> 00:05:46,705
so I won't kill you?

40
00:05:52,825 --> 00:05:53,825
Say something!

41
00:05:59,026 --> 00:06:00,705
We shouldn't end up like this.

42
00:06:03,066 --> 00:06:05,626
What exactly went wrong?

43
00:06:08,026 --> 00:06:09,506
What's wrong

44
00:06:11,746 --> 00:06:12,626
with me liking you?

45
00:06:17,626 --> 00:06:20,865
What's wrong
with me wanting to marry you?

46
00:06:23,906 --> 00:06:28,825
