51
00:07:07,385 --> 00:07:08,906
Not only did I agree with a smile,

52
00:07:09,746 --> 00:07:11,705
but I also offered the dowry personally.

53
00:07:13,506 --> 00:07:15,226
I agreed once

54
00:07:15,226 --> 00:07:17,226
and even agreed again.

55
00:07:19,746 --> 00:07:21,105
You wouldn't believe it.

56
00:07:21,946 --> 00:07:24,666
The whole world wouldn't believe it.

57
00:07:24,865 --> 00:07:25,425
Shut up.

58
00:07:25,746 --> 00:07:26,346
Shut up.

59
00:07:27,346 --> 00:07:28,425
Stop talking nonsense!

60
00:07:28,425 --> 00:07:30,385
Ever since the day
my mother committed suicide,

61
00:07:30,626 --> 00:07:32,705
I have chosen this path!

62
00:07:34,425 --> 00:07:35,536
I took advantage of you.

63
00:07:36,545 --> 00:07:37,825
I took advantage of myself.

64
00:07:39,506 --> 00:07:41,825
I married one woman after another.

65
00:07:43,506 --> 00:07:44,666
Every time I married,

66
00:07:46,865 --> 00:07:48,425
I didn't allow you
to say congratulations,

67
00:07:50,066 --> 00:07:51,825
and give me wedding gifts as well.

68
00:07:51,825 --> 00:07:53,265
Do you know why?

69
00:07:55,626 --> 00:07:57,666
I naively believed

70
00:07:58,346 --> 00:08:00,145
that as long as you
didn't congratulate me,

71
00:08:00,985 --> 00:08:01,946
I didn't receive

72
00:08:01,946 --> 00:08:03,906
your approval.

73
00:08:04,305 --> 00:08:06,226
Without your approval,

74
00:08:07,305 --> 00:08:08,666
all my marriage wasn't valid.

75
00:08:08,666 --> 00:08:09,626
Stop it.

76
00:08:09,666 --> 00:08:11,226
Believe it or not, I will kill you!

77
00:08:11,226 --> 00:08:12,786
If we can't be together
when being alive,

78
00:08:12,786 --> 00:08:15,186
let's die together.

79
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,385
You...

80
00:08:43,145 --> 00:08:43,760
You...

81
00:08:44,906 --> 00:08:45,488
You...

82
00:09:07,825 --> 00:09:08,546
Your Majesty.

83
00:09:09,385 --> 00:09:09,906
Your Majesty.

84
00:09:13,505 --> 00:09:15,466
Don't pull me.

85
00:09:16,026 --> 00:09:17,625
Let go of me.

86
00:09:18,466 --> 00:09:19,466
Take His Majesty away.

87
00:09:19,466 --> 00:09:20,666
No.

88
00:09:21,106 --> 00:09:22,306
I won't go.

89
00:09:22,306 --> 00:09:23,546
I won't go.

90
00:09:23,705 --> 00:09:24,745
You know too.

91
